SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`

    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)

    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE `p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1
LIMIT @__p_2

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE `p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1
LIMIT @__p_2

2024-08-24 11:41:19.824 +05:30 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__request_Username_0='?' (Size = 4000), @__request_CustomerCode_1='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT `c`.`Username`, `c`.`Password` AS `Secret`, `a`.`AppUserId`, `a`.`Firstname`, `a`.`Lastname`, `c0`.`CustomerId`, `c0`.`CustomerCode`, `c0`.`CustomerShortName`, `c0`.`CustomerName`, `l`.`LanguageCode`, `a0`.`AppUserRoleCode` AS `RoleCode`
FROM `AppUser` AS `a`
INNER JOIN `CustomerAppUser` AS `c` ON `a`.`AppUserId` = `c`.`AppUserId`
INNER JOIN `Customer` AS `c0` ON `c`.`CustomerId` = `c0`.`CustomerId`
INNER JOIN `Language` AS `l` ON `c`.`LanguageId` = `l`.`LanguageId`
INNER JOIN `AppUserRole` AS `a0` ON `c`.`AppUserRoleId` = `a0`.`AppUserRoleId`

INNER JOIN `CustomerAppUser` AS `c` ON `a`.`AppUserId` = `c`.`AppUserId`
INNER JOIN `Customer` AS `c0` ON `c`.`CustomerId` = `c0`.`CustomerId`
INNER JOIN `Language` AS `l` ON `c`.`LanguageId` = `l`.`LanguageId`
INNER JOIN `AppUserRole` AS `a0` ON `c`.`AppUserRoleId` = `a0`.`AppUserRoleId`
WHERE ((`c`.`Username` = @__request_Username_0) AND (`c0`.`CustomerCode` = @__request_CustomerCode_1)) AND `c`.`IsActive`
LIMIT 1

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`

    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (

    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`

    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`

) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`

WHERE `p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`

LIMIT @__p_3

) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`

    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`

    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`

    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`

    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`

WHERE `p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1
LIMIT @__p_2

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
INNER JOIN `Gender` AS `g` ON `p`.`GenderId` = `g`.`GenderId`
WHERE (`p`.`Firstname` LIKE @__Format_1) AND (`p`.`Lastname` LIKE @__Format_2)
LIMIT @__p_3

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p2`.`IdentityNumber`, `p2`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientIdentity` AS `p2`
    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (

    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`

SELECT `p`.`PatientId`, `p`.`PatientCode`, `p`.`Firstname`, `p`.`Middlename`, `p`.`Lastname`, `p`.`DateOfBirth`, `g`.`GenderName` AS `Gender`, `t`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`IdentityNumber`
FROM `Patient` AS `p`

    SELECT `p0`.`PatientId`, `p0`.`PhoneNumber`
    FROM `PatientPhone` AS `p0`
    WHERE `p0`.`IsActive`
) AS `t` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t`.`PatientId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `p1`.`EmailAddress`, `p1`.`PatientId`
    FROM `PatientEmail` AS `p1`
    WHERE `p1`.`IsActive`
) AS `t0` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t0`.`PatientId`

    WHERE `p2`.`IsActive`
) AS `t1` ON `p`.`PatientId` = `t1`.`PatientId`
